@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam ArrowColor #2C3E50
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #2C3E50
skinparam RectangleFontSize 13

title Subset Analysis: Computing Minimal Subsets via Transitive Closure

rectangle "**Auth UI**" as F #FFE0B2
rectangle "**Auth Service**" as D #C8E6C9
rectangle "**User Store**" as E #C8E6C9
rectangle "**Crypto Lib**" as B #BBDEFB
rectangle "**Logger**" as C #BBDEFB
rectangle "**Config**" as A #BBDEFB
rectangle "**Reporting**" as G #FFE0B2
rectangle "**Report Engine**" as H #C8E6C9

F -down-> D : <<uses>>
F -down-> C : <<uses>>
D -down-> E : <<uses>>
D -down-> B : <<uses>>
D -down-> C : <<uses>>
E -down-> A : <<uses>>
E -down-> C : <<uses>>
B -down-> A : <<uses>>
G -down-> H : <<uses>>
H -down-> E : <<uses>>
H -down-> C : <<uses>>

note as N1 #E8F8F5
  **Minimal Subset for Auth UI**
  Transitive closure from Auth UI:
  {Auth UI, Auth Service, User Store,
   Crypto Lib, Logger, Config}
  All six modules must be present
  for Auth UI to function correctly.
end note

note as N2 #FEF9E7
  **Minimal Subset for Reporting**
  Transitive closure from Reporting:
  {Reporting, Report Engine,
   User Store, Logger, Config}
